## ğŸ”§ Troubleshooting

**401 Unauthorized?**  
â†’ Verify `HACKERONE_USERNAME` and `HACKERONE_API_KEY`

**403 Forbidden?**  
â†’ You must be enrolled in the program to access details

**Rate Limited?**  
â†’ Slow down requests. Cache results. Use pagination smartly.

